<template>
<v-container>
  <v-row>
    <v-col cols="8">
        <v-data-table

            :items="desserts"
            hide-default-header
            hide-default-footer
            class="elevation-1"
        ></v-data-table>
    </v-col>
  </v-row>
</v-container>
</template>

<style scoped lang="scss">

</style>

        { text: 'Fat (g)', value: 'fat' },
